high_descs: Turn right and look up at the the cabinet near the ceiling.
Open the cabinet door on the right, take out the copper bottle and close the door.
Bring the bottle down and turn right for two steps, turn all the way around.
Put the bottle on top of the toilet tank, on the far left above the flushing handle.
Turn left for five steps, turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the bottle on the top right of the counter.
Turn right for four steps, turn right for two steps, turn around.
Put the bottle on the top of the toilet tank to the right of the copper bottle on the left.
anns.task_desc: Put two copper-colored bottles on top of the toilet tank.

high_descs: turn gaze up to face cabinet above toilet
pick up bottle from cabinet
walk to face toilet
put bottle on toilet tank top
walk left to face left hand counter of sinks
pick up bottle from counter
walk to face toilet
put bottle on toilet tank top
anns.task_desc: put two bottles on toilet tank top

high_descs: Turn to the right and look above the toilet.
Open the cabinet above the toilet and pull out a metal bottle.
Turn around in a circle.
Place the bottle on the left edge of the toilet tank.
Walk to the door then turn right toward the mirror.
Retrieve a second bottle from the far left on the sink.
Walk toward the toilet and turn in a circle at the end of the counter.
Place the second bottle between the two others on the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Place two bottles on the toilet tank.
